        aboutP3:'Based in Geneva, we operate across Switzerland and internationally, delivering projects of all scales — from boutique commercial fit-outs to large mixed-use developments.',
        s1title:'Build',s1sub:'From Groundwork to Handover',s1cta:'Start a build',
