        s2title:'Design',s2sub:'Architecture · Interiors · Technical',s2cta:'Start a design',
        s2desc:'From concept to construction drawings, we develop designs that are as technically rigorous as they are considered. We handle everything from planning applications to detailed interior specifications, ready for immediate execution.',
        s2i1:'Concept design & feasibility',s2i2:'Architectural drawings & permits',s2i3:'Interior spatial planning',s2i4:'Technical specifications & schedules',
        s3title:'Project Management',s3sub:'Planning · Coordination · Delivery',s3cta:'Talk to us',
